info.name: Tumblr Icons- Fall Out Boy
info.description: Changes icons (old or new) to fall out boy-related.
info.additionalInfo: ** After installing, you have to click edit and change the “applies to” from “Everything” to “URLs on the domain” and then type “tumblr.com” in the box and click save. If you install an update after that, you have to go in and change it again.
